\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Tab separated values (TSV)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This format is a generic text file format used for many different things.
 The main characteristic is that uses the tab character for separating fields
 and new line character/s for separating rows.
 All of the previous formats are based on it.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
It can be used to represent matrices, modules and tables.
\end_layout

